WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.702
Previously on <i>Defiance...</i>

00:01.738 --> 00:04.045
May I ask what business
you have in Defiance?

00:04.080 --> 00:05.846
I'm going
to kill all the humans

00:05.881 --> 00:08.148
and burn the disgusting place
to the ground.

00:08.183 --> 00:10.619
You and your wife
will act as my saboteurs,

00:10.653 --> 00:12.320
destroying Defiance from within.

00:12.355 --> 00:15.223
My mom and dad, they're
working as spies for the VC.

00:16.826 --> 00:18.460
[grunting]

00:18.494 --> 00:19.628
Go! Go!

00:23.199 --> 00:26.001
(Amanda) Datak Tarr, you've been found
guilty of high treason.

00:26.035 --> 00:27.569
You are sentenced to die.

00:27.603 --> 00:29.170
This town will turn on us

00:29.205 --> 00:31.006
if they learn
you're protecting a spy.

00:31.040 --> 00:33.208
You're more trouble
than you're worth.

00:33.242 --> 00:35.577
[gasps]

00:35.611 --> 00:36.578
[screams]

00:36.612 --> 00:38.813
Eat it.

00:38.848 --> 00:42.584
[dramatic music]

00:44.086 --> 00:46.688
We might just have the
beginnings of a strike force.

00:46.722 --> 00:48.256
We'll take the battle
to Rahm Tak,

00:48.290 --> 00:49.858
catch him with his pants down.

00:49.892 --> 00:52.827
Why is the Amazing Goddess
not fighting by their side?

00:54.063 --> 00:57.265
My daughter is not capable
of picking up a weapon.

00:57.299 --> 01:00.201
- I have to go back.
- No, not today.

01:00.236 --> 01:02.337
The endgame is coming,
my friends.

01:02.371 --> 01:06.441
In a few days,
we will ride into Defiance.

01:06.475 --> 01:10.512
Our Indogene lieutenant, Bebe,
has assumed a human face

01:10.546 --> 01:13.415
and has tunneled in
beneath the stasis nets.

01:13.449 --> 01:17.752
♪ ♪

01:23.359 --> 01:26.327
[exotic music]

01:26.362 --> 01:30.065
