24:52.813 --> 24:54.476
(Ranikar)
What is it?

24:54.510 --> 24:56.244
(Bebe)
I heard something.

24:56.279 --> 24:58.713
Stay here.

24:58.748 --> 25:01.516
I'm gonna go check in
with Nolan.

25:03.355 --> 25:04.986
Hold your position.

25:05.021 --> 25:08.123
Do not come forward
under any circumstance.

25:16.629 --> 25:18.833
All right, let's go.

25:21.016 --> 25:23.456
[twig snaps]

25:23.491 --> 25:25.874
Beckman, I told you
to hold position in the tunnel.

25:25.908 --> 25:26.875
[gasps]

25:26.909 --> 25:29.944
[grunting]

25:47.530 --> 25:49.631
[gasping]

25:49.665 --> 25:51.766
[grenade beeping]

25:51.801 --> 25:53.768
No.

25:53.803 --> 25:55.270
No!

26:04.046 --> 26:05.080
No!

26:07.650 --> 26:12.787
No! No! No!

26:12.822 --> 26:15.323
[panting]

26:15.358 --> 26:17.192
[groans]

26:17.226 --> 26:18.927
You stupid pink-skin.

26:18.961 --> 26:21.029
[grunting]

26:49.627 --> 26:53.728
Thank you for leading your men
to slaughter.

26:53.763 --> 26:57.198
Your head will make
a wonderful trophy for Rahm.

27:00.436 --> 27:03.071
