36:17.399 --> 36:20.401
[speaking native language]

36:23.138 --> 36:25.373
(Nolan)
Well, they didn't shoot him.

36:28.924 --> 36:30.491
He's clean.

36:31.678 --> 36:33.147
Welcome home, lover boy.

36:33.181 --> 36:34.782
I think he's in,

36:34.816 --> 36:36.651
but I can't be sure.

36:38.983 --> 36:41.393
Blow the nets.

36:41.428 --> 36:43.291
Blowing the nets.

36:43.325 --> 36:45.835
Tenser particles
will hit critical mass

36:45.870 --> 36:48.529
in four minutes and counting.

36:48.563 --> 36:50.429
[computer beeping]

36:55.250 --> 36:56.991
You look like a
little working class

36:57.026 --> 36:58.781
these days, aren't you?

36:58.816 --> 37:00.850
[laughter]

37:00.884 --> 37:03.553
The shaming rack
is a great equalizer.

37:03.587 --> 37:06.556
What diluted form
of the Shaming ceremony

37:06.590 --> 37:08.197
are they practicing
in Defiance?

37:08.232 --> 37:12.227
Your arms and legs
seem curiously attached.

37:12.262 --> 37:15.298
[laughter]

37:16.345 --> 37:18.267
They cut me down
to send me here

37:18.302 --> 37:21.304
with the mayor's
surrender terms.

37:24.308 --> 37:25.575
Why you?

37:25.609 --> 37:29.512
They assumed you'd shoot
whomever came out.

37:29.546 --> 37:31.747
Honestly, I'm surprised
you didn't.

37:31.782 --> 37:34.584
Call me
a sentimental old fart.

37:35.904 --> 37:37.899
These surrender terms
are garbage.

37:37.934 --> 37:39.455
I'm not gonna draw back,

37:39.489 --> 37:41.731
I'm not going
to provide a hostage,

37:41.766 --> 37:43.844
and I'm not going
to negotiate.

37:43.879 --> 37:45.862
You go back,
and you tell Amanda

37:45.896 --> 37:49.465
her only option
is to drop the nets.

37:51.488 --> 37:54.251
What are you still doing here?
Go.

37:54.286 --> 37:57.506
I'd like to stay.

37:57.541 --> 38:00.276
I kidnapped your son.

38:00.310 --> 38:01.467
I beat you senseless.

38:01.502 --> 38:04.080
I got you put
on a shaming rack.

38:04.115 --> 38:05.515
If I let you stay,

38:05.550 --> 38:09.328
you will try to kill me
the first time I turn my back.

38:09.363 --> 38:13.162
Your reputation for shrewdness
is clearly well deserved.

38:19.300 --> 38:23.637
But I promise you, General,

38:23.671 --> 38:27.296
I am a broken man,

38:27.331 --> 38:31.044
coming to you
in my hour of need.

38:36.351 --> 38:40.687
Granted, I like the humility.

38:40.722 --> 38:43.056
It pleases me.

38:44.637 --> 38:49.997
But I am not in a position

38:50.031 --> 38:51.738
to take any chances

38:51.773 --> 38:55.902
with victory so close at hand.

38:57.472 --> 39:00.307
May I prove my loyalty?

39:02.876 --> 39:05.812
I will require
my charge blade.

39:05.847 --> 39:07.414
[laughter]

39:07.448 --> 39:09.883
You want me to arm you?

39:09.917 --> 39:12.386
[scoffs]
I don't quite see the joke.

39:12.420 --> 39:16.256
I'm fighting
for my life, General.

39:16.291 --> 39:18.458
There is no joke.

39:23.563 --> 39:24.830
You...

39:27.735 --> 39:30.270
You push my buttons,
you know that?

39:30.305 --> 39:33.273
[orchestral music]

39:33.308 --> 39:37.946
♪ ♪

39:37.981 --> 39:39.982
Watch him.

39:48.323 --> 39:50.357
[computer beeps]

39:50.391 --> 39:51.792
The shaming rack
would have ripped

39:51.826 --> 39:54.227
my four limbs
from my body.

39:54.262 --> 39:58.195
You have rescued me
from this fate.

39:58.230 --> 40:00.133
Therefore, my body is yours.

40:00.168 --> 40:01.868
[all murmuring]

40:05.434 --> 40:08.408
Including my good left arm.

40:08.443 --> 40:10.310
[all yelling]

40:10.345 --> 40:14.314
Holy crap!

40:17.000 --> 40:20.387
That is some gangster-ass shit!
Oh!

40:20.421 --> 40:22.956
[yelling]

40:22.990 --> 40:25.659
(Rahm)
I am impressed!

40:25.693 --> 40:28.762
Wow!

40:28.796 --> 40:31.031
- I think he's in, right?
- (all) Yeah!

40:31.065 --> 40:34.201
I mean, on a probationary basis.

40:34.235 --> 40:36.336
Thank you, Favi Tak.

40:36.371 --> 40:38.872
May I take a moment alone?

40:38.906 --> 40:40.401
The pain is tremendous.

40:40.436 --> 40:42.075
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

40:42.110 --> 40:44.077
Don't go too far.

40:45.156 --> 40:48.348
Oh, my God!
Crazy-ass haint!

40:48.383 --> 40:51.952
This is definitely going
in the collection, right?

40:53.721 --> 40:56.456
